  "monster": {
    "title": "Ujewk.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Ujewk has a skeletal light grey body and a thin, worm-like head. It stinks of decay. It looks incredibly angry.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 191     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++ +   </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +         </lightgrey>                \n<darkgrey>    rF: ...     </darkgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ++.      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: ∞        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 130% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 91% to hit with your +9 quick blade of protection and 89% to hit with your bite.\nIt has about 76% to hit you.\n\nAttack                 Max Damage      \nSpore: electric touch  48 + 20 (elec)  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.",
